{"tid":905581,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係𨋢聽到個老豆話個女係雞","createTime":"2018-11-17T08:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T09:26:40.000Z","uid":130894,"like":9,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aab5a1bf037b5dc37310d640238a42e99b5b35c7","tid":905581,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"話說頭先係部𨋢聽到以下對話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 目測十令歲既小妹妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆: 唔知上面有咩game玩呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小妹妹: 啲game會唔會好小學雞架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆: 妳而家唔係雞咩？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小妹妹: 我中一啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆: 中一咪又係雞！你估你大學雞？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小妹妹: 將來我大個就係大學雞！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆: 係你先好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我: wtf？<br />\n<br />\n我到底聽左啲乜野？我到而家都成頭問號...<br />\n個老豆係咪假膠黎？我係𨋢真係尷尬到想縮入對襪個隆度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7ec0714b076c0864b667257d3c07a6e1daf72a","tid":905581,"uid":63864,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"人地父女傾下計<br />\n你就諗埋呢d on9 野"},{"pid":"4b51d65dac537ce095ef4e18049fb2344cf87378","tid":905581,"uid":37054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:50:06.000Z","ms